abusinessl: Vietnam Dairy Products Joint Stock Co is a producer and wholesaler of dairy products headquartered in Vietnam. The company's products include dairy products such as liquid and powdered milk, value-added dairy products such as condensed milk, drinking and spoon yoghurt, ice cream, and cheese which serve clients in Vietnam, Australia, Cambodia, Iraq, the Philippines and the United States. The company's brands include Vinamilk, Dielac, V-fresh, Coffee Moment and Condensed Milk. The company was founded in 1976.
tbusinessl: Lao - Jagro Development Xiengkhowang Co Ltd is a dairy cattle farming establishment. The Company is located in Laos.

abusinessl: Bank of China Hong Kong (Holdings) Ltd, located in Central Hong Kong, Hong Kong is a bank offering residential mortgage, wealth management and credit cards, lending, SME lending and trade finance, cash management and financial institution services. The Company has 280 branches and about 440 ATMs and other delivery channels in Hong Kong.
